            value: '<h3 data-block-key="a4yft"><b>Flexibility in learning</b></h3><p data-block-key="9r9c4">One of the primary reasons Nic and his family find OpenStax invaluable is the freedom it provides in learning. OpenStax places the information front and center, empowering learners to absorb it in their preferred manner. “You&#x27;re not struggling through decade-old video clips, you&#x27;re not getting bombarded with completion reminders, you&#x27;re not worrying about whether or not you vibe with the instructor,&quot; Nic said.</p>',
